com.delphix.masking.api.provider

Interface LogService

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DriverSupportLogService, MaskingLogService

    public interface LogService
    This is the interface Delphix Masking Log Service must implement. Attention! When using logger - be careful in choosing the logged information. The sensitive information (to be masked) should never be logged!
